            <li><strong>Routing/Controllers</strong>: `AdminController` groups admin routes; `EventController` handles CRUD; routes defined with attributes.</li>
            <li><strong>Code Quality</strong>: Reusable partials, meaningful names, validation on entity, and tidy templates.</li>
            <li><strong>Progress</strong>: Admin dashboard KPIs, charts, and recent events wired to database.</li>
